name: CI Global Alpha Innovation ETF
longDescription: CINVs investment objective is to obtain maximum long-term capital growth from an actively managed portfolio that primarily invests in equity and equity-related securities of companies from around the world that are positioned to benefit from innovations and advancements in technology, products, processes or services.
